data.description: Welcome to your new home adjacent to Bide a Wee Golf Course! The location of this property is truly unbeatable, nestled in a cul-de-sac for added privacy. With its well-maintained features, thoughtful layout, and prime location, it's a haven waiting for you to call it home. This ranch was upgraded to include an owner's suite equaling 4 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms. Schedule a showing today and experience the warmth and comfort this property has to offer!
